---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import aboutImage from '../../assets/images/about-me-image.jpg';
import '../../assets/styles/AboutMe.css';
---

<div class="about-section" id="aboutme">
  <h2>ABOUT ME</h2>
  <div class="row align-items-center">
    <div class="about-image">
      <Image src={aboutImage} alt="Casey Hsu" />
    </div>
    <div class="about-text">
      <p>
        Hey there! I'm currently a JavaScript developer focused on building reliable sites for
        e-commerce and agency clients. Most of my work is in <strong>Shopify</strong>, <strong>HubSpot CMS</strong>, and <strong>WordPress</strong>, with React/Next.js frontends and Node.js backends.
      </p>
      <p>
        Before tech, I spent nine years leading culinary teams, which taught me how to stay calm under pressure, communicate clearly, and deliver on deadlines. I'm a George Brown Computer Programming and Analysis honours grad, a <strong>Contentful Certified Professional</strong>, and I build day to day with JavaScript, TypeScript, Docker, and modern AI-assisted workflows.
      </p>
      <p>
        I'm currently open to full-time roles in the Greater Toronto Area, including hybrid and on-site opportunities.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
